channel.title: WebShell
channel.description: I've made the base for an online command prompt. No idea what use it could have. Working version at http://www.jwarez.net/sh/ Try typing 'date' or 'help' or 'hai' and see what happens ;) It works using JavaScript, PHP, and Iframes. If you want the source code PM me. Note: This is useless crap and should not be considered purposeful by any means.
